OL,7,FTwo care workers have been charged
OL,8,Fafter the BBC's Panorama programme
OL,9,Ffilmed patients allegedly being
OL,10,Fmistreated at a NHS mental health unit.
OL,12,FSupport worker Sheryl Price, 45, of
OL,13,FEldergreen Close, Bolton, has been
OL,14,Fcharged with 14 counts of ill-
OL,15,Ftreatment against four alleged victims
OL,16,Fat The Edenfield Centre in Prestwich,
OL,17,FGreater Manchester.
