OL,7,FNurse Sara Coleman, 43, of Mitford
OL,8,FStreet, Stretford, has been charged
OL,9,Fwith five counts of ill-treatment
OL,10,Fagainst four alleged victims.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police said in a
OL,13,Fstatement that the charges follow an
OL,14,Finvestigation launched in 2022.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Julie Adams said:
OL,17,F"Since 2022, we have been actively
OL,18,Finvestigating several allegations
OL,19,Frelating to The Edenfield Centre,
OL,20,Ffollowing a period of undercover
OL,21,Ffiling at the mental health unit.
