OL,7,F"We have now charged two suspects in
OL,8,Frelation to this, and they will appear
OL,9,Fat court in the new year.
OL,11,F"Since this incident was brought to
OL,12,Four attention, we have been working
OL,13,Fwith partner agencies to ensure that
OL,14,Fpatients were safeguarded and to
OL,15,Finvestigate criminality.
OL,17,F"Anyone who has concerns about care
OL,18,Fthey or a loved one has received
OL,19,Fshould contact us or Crimestoppers."
