OL,7,FNHS England commissioned an
OL,8,Findependent review of the trust
OL,9,Frunning the unit, Greater Manchester
OL,10,FMental Health NHS Foundation (GMMH),
OL,11,Ffollowing the BBC expose broadcast in
OL,12,FSeptember 2022.
OL,14,FThe programme showed patients being
OL,15,Fmocked, humiliated, bullied,
OL,16,Frestrained inappropriately and
OL,17,Fsecluded for long periods.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
