OL,7,FThe independent review, published in
OL,8,FJanuary 2024, found poor leadership,
OL,9,Fwith bosses "disconnected" from
OL,10,Freality.
OL,12,FThe review found the unit had chronic
OL,13,Fstaff shortages, low morale, a high
OL,14,Fturnover of staff and workers who felt
OL,15,F"exasperated" at not being listened to.
OL,17,FPatients and families told the report
OL,18,Fauthors they were not believed when
OL,19,Fthey raised concerns or complained
OL,20,Fabout care standards.
