OL,5,Cunit
OL,7,FThe review made 11 recommendations on
OL,8,Fpatient care, clinical leadership,
OL,9,Fculture, workforce and governance.
OL,11,FJan Ditheridge, chief executive at
OL,12,FGMMH, apologised after the release of
OL,13,Fthe review and said an improvement
OL,14,Fplan was in place to address the
OL,15,Fissues raised.
OL,17,FThe two workers have been bailed to
OL,18,Fappear at Manchester Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on 25 March 2026.
